parameters.name: CurrentPage
parameters.description: The page number. Default value: **1**. Pages start from page 1.

parameters.name: EndTimeStamp
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. The value is a UNIX timestamp.

parameters.name: Lang
parameters.description:
The language of the content within the request and response. Default value: **zh**. Valid values:

*   **zh**: Chinese
*   **en**: English

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries per page. Default value: 20. If you leave this parameter empty, 20 entries are returned on each page.

>  We recommend that you do not leave this parameter empty.

parameters.name: SrcIp
parameters.description: The source IP address of the attack.

parameters.name: StartTimeStamp
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. The value is a UNIX timestamp.
